132
00:12:10,520 --> 00:12:18,160
 ♫ In the darkness, I lose my way ♫ 

133
00:12:34,420 --> 00:12:41,380
 ♫ The music plays in the city's churches ♫ 

134
00:12:41,380 --> 00:12:47,820
 ♫ I should've been with you forever ♫ 

135
00:12:47,820 --> 00:12:51,220
 ♫ But it can't last when there's chaos ♫ 

136
00:12:51,220 --> 00:12:55,500
 ♫ And when I look back,
there is just rubble and empty alleys ♫ 

137
00:12:55,500 --> 00:13:02,780
 ♫ Who would've thought that
lovers would be torn apart by fate? ♫ 

138
00:13:03,660 --> 00:13:10,820
 ♫ You, like the breeze and the bright moon ♫ 

139
00:13:10,820 --> 00:13:16,980
 ♫ Are my companion through this life's struggles ♫ 

140
00:13:16,980 --> 00:13:20,400
 ♫ I hope your future is safe and sound ♫ 

141
00:13:20,400 --> 00:13:25,100
 ♫ That's my only wish ♫ 

142
00:13:25,667 --> 00:13:27,810
 ♫ Forget it ♫ 

143
00:13:27,810 --> 00:13:30,500
 ♫ It doesn't matter ♫ 

144
00:13:30,500 --> 00:13:35,780
 ♫ It really doesn't matter ♫ 

